170
00:11:29,200 --> 00:11:33,512
- Tu veux un dessert?
- Non, je ne veux pas de dessert.

171
00:11:34,680 --> 00:11:36,033
D'accord.

172
00:11:39,320 --> 00:11:41,390
Écoute, Carrie.

173
00:11:52,440 --> 00:11:54,078
Je sais que tu...

174
00:11:55,400 --> 00:11:58,551
